             was indicted for <rs id="t18291029-131-off725" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18291029-131-off725" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18291029-131-off725" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18291029-131-cd726" type="crimeDate">12th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291029-131-off725 t18291029-131-cd726"></join>, 1 watch, value 20s.; 1 ring, value 10s.; 1 diamond-pin, value 15s.; 12 sovereigns, 1 half-sovereign, 5 half-crowns, 9 shillings, 2 sixpences, and 1 5l. Bank note, the property of 
                     <persName id="t18291029-131-victim1076" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Partington
                     <interp inst="t18291029-131-victim1076" type="surname" value="Partington"></interp>
